snippet.title: Pincrediball DEMO launch trailer, March 2023
snippet.description:
This is the launch trailer for the DEMO version of Pincrediball: The Automata Pinball Wizard Game! This game was created as a sabbatical project. And who knows... given enough interest we might even complete it into a full game some time!

Timestamps:

0:00 Gameplay introduction
0:14 Further gameplay demos
0:34 Fast-forwarded gameplay & multiball
1:07 End slide with details
